description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 71, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 71, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Leverage for East, 3 for South, and Leverage for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50711-56362-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
